* Odvratno* je mirisalo iz čaše. (It was repulsive smell coming out of the glass.)

Ne volim da se češljam jer je to *odvratno*. (I don't like to comb my hair because it is repulsive.)

Njegovo ponašanje je bilo *odvratno*. (His behaviour was repulsive.)

Bio je *odvratno* zloban prema svima. (He was repulsively mean to everyone.)

Njegovi razgovori su bili *odvratni*. (His conversations were repulsive.)